Title: Orchard Themes
Description: Orchard Themes project hosts a variety of open source themes for the Orchard CMS project. Currently only a skeleton theme is included. Feel free to modify this one and submit it back, or submit your own theme to be added to the package.

Project Description
Orchard Themes project hosts a variety of open source themes for the Orchard CMS project.

This project is hosted by Setiri Group, as part of the Amazify project.
